🔷 setTimeout vs setImmediate

```javascript id="3mctf1"
setTimeout(() => console.log("Timeout"), 0);
setImmediate(() => console.log("Immediate"));
```

📌 Order may vary
📌 Depends on event loop phase

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 process.nextTick()

```javascript id="aqkg4j"
process.nextTick(() => {
  console.log("Next Tick");
});
```

✔ Runs before Promises
✔ Highest priority

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 Priority Order

```text id="5bd5sh"
1. process.nextTick()
2. Promises (microtasks)
3. setTimeout / setImmediate
```

