🔷 Blocking vs Event Loop

Blocking code:

```javascript id="p5gwwu"
fs.readFileSync("file.txt");
```

❌ Blocks event loop

---

Non-blocking:

```javascript id="xghbq6"
fs.readFile("file.txt", callback);
```

✔ Event loop continues

